Meet <b>Peter</b>, our citizen of the week!<br><br>Peter lives at <a href='/home/?user=peterjtong'>92267 Park Avenue</a> in one of Metro Park's newly redesigned duplexes.  He really likes the short commute to <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/main_map.phtml?location=downtown">Downtown Millsberry</a> that living in Metro Park gives him, and the fast-paced lifestyle of his neighborhood is one of the things that lured him there when he moved in on March 5, 2006.<br><br>Peter is already well known at <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/academy">Millsberry Academy</a> and around town for his athleticism, since one rarely sees such a wide range of athletic abilities like those he possesses.  Peter's equally comfortable on the basketball court, the football field, or in the pool.  On weekends, Peter can often be found in <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/peabody_park">Peabody Park</a>, leading his team down the field in a game of touch football or setting up plays as a point guard in a pickup basketball game.  He's easy to spot on the court, because he's usually wearing his lucky red, gold, and silver jersey.<br><br>Since he understands the importance of a well-balanced life, Peter also puts lots of effort into being a good student.  He has a very curious mind, which is why he always asks plenty of questions in class.  Peter's favorite subject in school is math, and he really enjoys learning new formulas and figuring out ways to apply them to everyday situations.<br><br>When Peter needs a break from sports and academics, he likes to hang out at his best friend's house.  They enjoy talking about their favorite baseball team, the Millsberry Millers, discussing recent events at <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/academy/">Millsberry Academy</a>, and listening to the newest music releases.  Peter especially likes rap and pop songs, because their upbeat tempos help to keep him energized throughout the day.<br><br>Thanks for being a fine citizen, Peter, and congratulations on being named Millsberry's citizen of the week!</div>
